### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/pets
@userEmail = user@example.com

### 1. Crear mascota - Rex (Perro)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rex",
  "type": "Perro",
  "userEmail": "{{userEmail}}"
}

### 2. Crear mascota - Michi (Gato)
POST {{baseUrl}}
